com.psddev.dari.db

Class CompoundPredicate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psddev.dari.db.Record
      • com.psddev.dari.db.Predicate
        • com.psddev.dari.db.CompoundPredicate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Recordable, HtmlObject, Cloneable, Comparable<Record>

    public final class CompoundPredicate
extends Predicate
    Predicate whose evaluation depends on its child predicates. This class is immutable as long as all child predicates are immutable as well.
